  "detailed_description": "<h1>Special Offer</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1174270/extras/93bbbe9b86a564840107613b7f337c95.avif?t=1685759770\" width=600 height=328 /></span><br><br>IKO 39 offers the player, along with the main character, engineer Casey, to go to the planet Morrow, which has stopped communicating with Earth.<br>Arriving on the planet we will face a number of problems:<br><br>- repair of the ship with the search for batteries to it;<br>- constant lack of oxygen;<br>- by the evil elements of the station, who are trying to kill us;<br>- sandstorms that interfere with visibility;<br>- you constantly have to take control of different station devices (drone and other elements);<br>- we will have to investigate what happened at the station with the help of holographic blocks of memories and diaries of the station manager.<br>- and other problems of the station that lie in wait for our heroine.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1174270/extras/29bb66fc9c3001a2264fc81f12cc1f78.poster.avif?t=1685759770\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1174270/extras/29bb66fc9c3001a2264fc81f12cc1f78.webm?t=1685759770\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1174270/extras/29bb66fc9c3001a2264fc81f12cc1f78.mp4?t=1685759770\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>And in the end, we have to find out what happened at the IKO 39 station with its inhabitants.</strong>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1174270/extras/93bbbe9b86a564840107613b7f337c95.avif?t=1685759770\" width=600 height=328 /></span><br><br>IKO 39 offers the player, along with the main character, engineer Casey, to go to the planet Morrow, which has stopped communicating with Earth.<br>Arriving on the planet we will face a number of problems:<br><br>- repair of the ship with the search for batteries to it;<br>- constant lack of oxygen;<br>- by the evil elements of the station, who are trying to kill us;<br>- sandstorms that interfere with visibility;<br>- you constantly have to take control of different station devices (drone and other elements);<br>- we will have to investigate what happened at the station with the help of holographic blocks of memories and diaries of the station manager.<br>- and other problems of the station that lie in wait for our heroine.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1174270/extras/29bb66fc9c3001a2264fc81f12cc1f78.poster.avif?t=1685759770\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1174270/extras/29bb66fc9c3001a2264fc81f12cc1f78.webm?t=1685759770\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1174270/extras/29bb66fc9c3001a2264fc81f12cc1f78.mp4?t=1685759770\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>And in the end, we have to find out what happened at the IKO 39 station with its inhabitants.</strong>",
